Class InvalidContent

All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, Content, Serializable
public class InvalidContent
extends BaseContent

This class acts as a placekeeper for Content objects that have some underlying error associated with their construction. A Source may return an instance of InvalidContent for problematic Datasets.

See Also:
Serialized Form
